Subject: SQL Database server disk space
Description: We keep running out of disk space every few months. How can I verify old data is being purged and we are not just keeping everything?
What_We_Know__c: No clear reason for the SEEK scans only to not complete when FSAA and FACS jobs via the same Proxy are working for the the multiple host/Job groups.
Solution_Comment__c:
Post the upgraded and Bulk import workarounds form the other Scan cases the data per the Activity View is only showing the last 90 days.
TSQL used to confirm.
SELECT * FROM [StealthAudit].[dbo].[SA_FSAC_ActivityEventsView]
